{"_id":"NDFiNTQzZjk5YjY1","name":"Wand of Web","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZmI0Y2RjY2RkYmM1","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":55,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":550000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Wand of Web</h4>Wand, uncommon (requires attunement by a spellcaster)<br><br>This wand has 7 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges to cast the <i><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Item data-id=YzFlNzgwODU4Yjlh ><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i>web</a></i> spell (save DC 15) from it.<br><br>The wand regains 1d6 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the wand crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.<br>","img":"worlds/dragon-heist/journal/007_-_Magic_Items/055_-_Wand_of_Web/avatar_1.png"}
