{"_id":"YTFhODFmNmE4ZWMx","name":"Credits","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ODA2YWZiMTg2MDg1","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":2,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":20000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<p><b>Lead Designer:</b> Christopher Perkins<br><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Designers:</b> James J. Haeck, James Introcaso, Adam Lee,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">Matt Sernett<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Rules Development:</b> Jeremy Crawford, Ben Petrisor, Kate Welch<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Story Consultants:</b> Matthew Mercer, Charles Sanders</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Managing Editor:</b> Jeremy Crawford<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Lead Editor:</b> Christopher Perkins<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Editors:</b> Michele Carter, Scott Fitzgerald Gray, Kim Mohan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Art Director:</b> Kate Irwin<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Additional Art Direction:</b> Shauna Narciso, Richard Whitters<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Graphic Designer:</b> Emi Tanji<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Cover Illustrator:</b> Tyler Jacobson<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Interior Illustrators:</b> Mark Behm, Eric Belisle, Zoltan Boros, Clint Cearley, Sidharth Chaturvedi, Daarken, Eric Deschamps, Olga Drebas, Leesha Hannigan, Ralph Horsley, Tyler Jacobson, Sam Keiser, Julian Kok, Alayna Lemmer, Christopher Moeller, Scott Murphy, Jim Pavelec, Claudio Pozas, Vincent Proce, Ned Rogers, Craig J Spearing, Jason Thompson, Cory Trego-Erdner, Richard Whitters, Mark Winters, Shawn Wood, Bayard Wu, Kieran Yanner<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><b>Interior Cartographer:</b> Dyson Logos<br></span><b style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">Poster