{"_id":"ZmJiOTI5YzAzN2U3","name":"Potion of Animal Friendship","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MDUzY2I1NGRkMjQ3","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":0,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":0,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Potion of Animal Friendship</h4><i>Potion, uncommon</i><br><br>When you drink this potion, you can cast the <i><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Item data-id=NGRjNTJhZjQ5NDI3 ><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i>animal friendship</a></i> spell (save DC 13) for 1 hour at will. Agitating this muddy liquid brings little bits into view: a fish scale, a hummingbird tongue, a cat claw, or a squirrel hair.<br>","img":""}
